{"id": "1", "input_text": "“王大爷早啊，昨晚睡得怎么样？来，先测个血压。嗯……血压是一百三十八、八十二，稍微有点高啊。体温我看看，三十六度七，挺正常的。我看你这心电监护，心率七十五，呼吸十八次。一会儿记得把早饭吃了，药别忘了吃。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "36.7", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "75", "respiratoryRate": "18", "bloodPressure": "138/82", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "2", "input_text": "“十二床李姐，手术回来三个小时了。现在感觉怎么样？刀口疼得厉害吗？血氧饱和度是九十八，挺好。心率快一点，九十二次，呼吸二十次。体温三十七度二，有点低热是正常的。皮肤切口我看了一下，目前是完好的，没有渗血。保持这个姿势别乱动啊。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "37.2", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "92", "respiratoryRate": "20", "bloodPressure": null, "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": "手术切口", "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "3", "input_text": "“检查一下十五床。患者目前处于嗜睡状态，能唤醒。来，看我手电筒。左侧瞳孔三毫米，对光反射灵敏；右侧瞳孔也是三毫米，对光反射灵敏。血压一百二十六、七十四，心率六十八。继续观察神志变化，要是发现呕吐立刻叫我。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "68", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "126/74", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": "嗜睡", "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "4", "input_text": "“张叔，今天觉得胸闷好点没？吸上氧气感觉怎么样？我看下，氧流量开的是每分钟两升。现在的血氧是九十四，呼吸频率还是快，二十四次。体温三十八度五，还在发烧。脉搏一百零二。这一瓶水吊完记得叫我，我再给你测个腋温。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "38.5", "pulseRate": "102", "heartRate": null, "respiratoryRate": "24", "bloodPressure": null, "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": "静脉通路", "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "5", "input_text": "“核对一下三号床的入量出量。家属，刚才那瓶生理盐水五百毫升已经输完了是吧？记录一下，静脉入量五百。我看下尿袋，尿量大概是三百五十毫升，颜色是淡黄色的，挺清亮。今天病人喝水了吗？记得喂点水，晚点我再来记总数。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": null, "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": null, "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": "静脉通路、导尿管", "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": "异常", "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "6", "input_text": "“五零八房的老刘，今天空腹体重测了吗？七十二点五公斤是吧，比前天轻了点。来，手平放。血压是一百五、九十五，还是没降下来啊。脉搏八十五次。你这个降压药是不是没按时吃？心率挺整齐的，但血压得控制住，不然容易头晕。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": "85", "heartRate": null, "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "150/95", "weight": "72.5", "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "7", "input_text": "“接个班，急诊刚送来一位。男性，四十五岁。到达时意识模糊，BP九十、六十，脉搏一百一十，呼吸二十六。已经建立了静脉通道，目前正在吸氧。瞳孔是对称的，大概二点五左右，对光反射迟钝。病史提供人是家属，初步诊断是失血性休克。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": "失血性休克", "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": "110", "heartRate": null, "respiratoryRate": "26", "bloodPressure": "90/60", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": "模糊", "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": "静脉通路", "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "8", "input_text": "“阿婆，来量个体温。三十六度八，不烧了。心率是幺零八，怎么这么快？是不是刚才动弹了？呼吸二一次。血压是一百二、八十六。我看你这皮肤有点破损，是在哪儿蹭的吗？一会儿我给你涂点药。记得多喝温开水啊。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "36.8", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "108", "respiratoryRate": "21", "bloodPressure": "120/86", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": "破损", "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "9", "input_text": "“小宝贝今天乖不乖呀？医生叔叔听听心跳。心率比较快，一百一十五次，小朋友紧张。体温三十九度幺，还是高热。呼吸三十次，肺部听诊有点杂音。家属记得多物理降温，要是还是烧得这么厉害，我们要考虑换个抗生素了。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "39.1", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "115", "respiratoryRate": "30", "bloodPressure": null, "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "10", "input_text": "“最后巡一下病房。二十号床，还没睡呢？血氧监控我看一下，九十六，正常。心率六十二，呼吸十六。我看你这引流袋，出量大概五十毫升，血性液体。体温刚才护士量过是三十七度。早点休息吧，有什么不舒服按床头铃。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "37.0", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "62", "respiratoryRate": "16", "bloodPressure": null, "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": "引流管", "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "11", "input_text": "“二十八床，现在胸闷的感觉缓解点没？我看硝酸甘油泵入的速度是每小时三毫升。量下血压，一百一十、七十，比刚才降下来点。心率六十四次，挺稳的。如果待会儿觉得头晕或者心慌，一定要立刻按铃，药量我们再调。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "64", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "110/70", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": "静脉通路", "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "12", "input_text": "“王阿姨，测个餐后血糖啊。诶，十一点二，还是有点高。早上的诺和锐打了十二个单位对吧？体温正常，三十六度四。下午记得别吃水果了。我看你脚踝这儿有点水肿，平时坐着的时候把腿抬高一点。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "36.4", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": null, "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": null, "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": "11.2", "consciousness": null, "skin": "其他", "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "13", "input_text": "“一号床，今天开始输头孢曲松了，观察一下有没有皮疹或者胸闷。体温还是高，三十八度九，心率九十五。呼吸频率二十二次，血氧九十三，稍微低了点，把氧气流量调到三升每分钟。痰咳得出来吗？颜色是什么样的？”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "38.9", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "95", "respiratoryRate": "22", "bloodPressure": null, "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": "静脉通路", "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "14", "input_text": "“七床，今天还恶心吗？这瓶潘托拉唑是保护胃黏膜的，点滴速度别自己调啊。血压一百零五、六十五，脉搏七十二。昨晚到现在一共喝了五百毫升水，记录一下。我看尿色有点深，还得再多补点液。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": "72", "heartRate": null, "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "105/65", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": "静脉通路", "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": "异常", "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "15", "input_text": "“老张，把手握紧我看看。嗯，左边还是没劲。昨晚吃的阿司匹林和阿托伐他汀没反应吧？瞳孔两点五毫米，对光反射灵敏。血压一百四十二、九十，心率七十八。一定要按时吃药，预防血栓再次形成。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "78", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "142/90", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": "异常", "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "16", "input_text": "“十六床，早上给你打了一针呋塞米。刚才那两个小时尿了多少？六百毫升是吧，好，记录在出量里。体重今天测的是六十八公斤。血压一百三十五、八十五。注意听，如果觉得耳朵响或者身上没力气，及时跟我们说。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": null, "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "135/85", "weight": "68", "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "17", "input_text": "“四十五床，手术后止痛泵带着呢吧？要是还觉得疼，我们刚才加了地佐辛。测下呼吸，十四次，稍微有点慢，要注意。心率八十二，血氧九十九。我看你这引流管里是淡红色的液体，量不多，大概三十毫升，先观察。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "82", "respiratoryRate": "14", "bloodPressure": null, "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": "引流管", "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "18", "input_text": "“快，建立双通路！心率掉到四十了，推一毫克肾上腺素！血压七十、四十，赶紧挂上多巴胺，每小时十毫克泵入。准备气管插管。血氧测不到，快，心肺复苏别停！记录时间，十四点一十分。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 14:10:00", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "40", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "70/40", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": "静脉通路", "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "19", "input_text": "“十二床，明天手术。刚才给你皮下注射了低分子肝素，预防血栓的。血压一百二十八、七十二，心率七十。体温三十六度六，没发烧。晚八点以后就不要吃东西了，水也少喝，听清楚了吗？”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "36.6", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "70", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "128/72", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "20", "input_text": "“陈大爷，这颗是地高辛，专门稳心率的；那颗是氨氯地平，降压用的。别吃混了。我看下现在的脉搏，六十八次，挺规律的。血压一百三、八十，控制得不错。记得药要用温开水送服，别用茶水啊。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": "68", "heartRate": null, "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "130/80", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "21", "input_text": "“快，二号床怀疑脑出血。意识深昏迷，对光反射消失，左侧瞳孔五毫米，右侧两毫米，不对称。血压极高，二百一、一百二。赶紧推二百五十毫升甘露醇，二十分钟内滴完。心率五十六，呼吸慢，十二次。记录好，准备急诊手术。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "56", "respiratoryRate": "12", "bloodPressure": "210/120", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": "深昏迷", "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": "静脉通路", "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "22", "input_text": "“三十六床支架做完了。今天的波立维和阿司匹林都吃了吧？量下血压，一百一、六十八。心率七十二。我看你腹股沟穿刺点皮肤有点破损和青紫，大概三乘三厘米的淤斑。多压一会儿，别急着下地。血氧九十七。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": "支架术后", "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "72", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "110/68", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": "破损、其他", "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "23", "input_text": "“张大爷，呼吸机戴好了，别漏气。现在的参数是每分钟吸氧五升。血氧维持在九十一，呼吸还是快，二十八次。心率一百一十。体温三十七度八。记录一下，刚才咳了大概二十毫升黄脓痰，性状比较粘稠。待会做个雾化。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "37.8", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "110", "respiratoryRate": "28", "bloodPressure": null, "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "24", "input_text": "“老李，测血糖。餐后十四点六。你这二甲双胍一天吃几次？血压一百三十、八十二。心率七十六。昨天的总出量记一下，尿量两千三百毫升。我看你这双下肢皮肤还算完好，但有点干，记得涂点润肤的。体温三十六度五。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "36.5", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "76", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "130/82", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": "14.6", "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "25", "input_text": "“十八床，牵引疼得厉害吗？给你开了塞来昔布口服。血压一百二、七十五，心率八十。重点看下骶尾部皮肤，长期卧床容易出问题。嗯，目前皮肤完好。体温三十七度幺。记得每两小时翻一次身，家属搭把手。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "37.1", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "80", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "120/75", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": "异常", "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "26", "input_text": "“接班，八号床。目前处于镇静状态。多巴胺每小时八毫克泵入，咪达唑仑每小时三毫升。过去四小时尿量一百五十。血压九十五、五十八，心率九十二，血氧九十五。皮肤背部有一处破损。引流管出量十毫升，色淡红。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "92", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "95/58", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": "药物镇静状", "skin": "破损", "limbActivity": null, "catheter": "静脉通路、引流管", "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "27", "input_text": "“急查！患者刚才呕血了，大概三百毫升，颜色咖啡色。血压掉到八十五、五十五。心率一百二十。立刻建立双通路，静脉滴注奥美拉唑。血氧九十二，呼吸二十四。赶紧联系输血科，准备配血！”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "120", "respiratoryRate": "24", "bloodPressure": "85/55", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": "静脉通路", "diet": "异常", "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "28", "input_text": "“小朋友，不哭不哭。体温三十八度五，体重十五公斤。给头孢西丁，剂量零点七五克。心率一百一十，呼吸二十六。血氧九十九。家属注意看孩子嘴唇紫不紫，有情况叫护士。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "38.5", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "110", "respiratoryRate": "26", "bloodPressure": null, "weight": "15", "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "29", "input_text": "“四号床，明天肠道手术。今天要做清洁灌肠。血压一百二、八十，心率七十四，体温三十六度三。由于要禁食，今天入量主要是静脉补液，一共一千五百毫升。意识清醒。有什么紧张的随时跟我说。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "36.3", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "74", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "120/80", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": "清楚", "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": "静脉通路", "diet": "异常", "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "30", "input_text": "“二十二床，今天打第二针地塞米松，促进宝宝肺部发育。血压一百四十、九十二，有点高，注意休息。心率八十八，血氧九十八。胎心监测一百四十五次。没觉得头晕吧？要是觉得眼睛看东西模糊立刻叫我。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "88", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "140/92", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "31", "input_text": "“做完介入回来了。意识清醒。血压一百三十、八十，心率六十八。我摸一下足背动脉，搏动对称。穿刺部位皮肤完好，加压包扎中。血氧九十九。这六个小时一定要平卧，腿千万不能弯，知道吗？”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": "介入术后", "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "68", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "130/80", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": "清楚", "skin": "手术切口", "limbActivity": "异常", "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "32", "input_text": "“老王，透析前的体重是八十二公斤。血压一百六、九十五。心率八十二。等下透析中会用到低分子肝素钙，预防滤器凝血。体温三十六度七。有没有觉得哪里痒或者身上起疹子？”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "36.7", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "82", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "160/95", "weight": "82", "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "33", "input_text": "“九床，今天上顺铂化疗。为了水化，入量要达到三千毫升。血压一百一、七十，心率七十五。如果觉得恶心，我们刚才给了昂丹司琼。血氧九十七。注意看尿量，如果尿少了或者变色了，赶紧说。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "75", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "110/70", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": "静脉通路", "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "34", "input_text": "“阿公，吃早饭了。这颗阿卡波糖要跟着第一口饭一起嚼碎。血压量一下，一百二、七十。心率六十四。体温三十六度五。我看你这腿上皮肤有点破损，是不是自己抓的？不要抓，容易感染。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "36.5", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "64", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "120/70", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": "破损", "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "35", "input_text": "“十五床，前列腺术后。现在是持续膀胱冲洗。冲洗液入量每小时五百毫升。看下出量，引流液是淡红色，比较清亮。血压一百二十五、八十，心率七十二。血氧九十八。意识清醒。引流管保持通畅。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": "前列腺术后", "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "72", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "125/80", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": "清楚", "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": "导尿管、引流管", "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": "异常", "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "36", "input_text": "“挂号幺零二号，高热惊厥。体温四十度二，脉搏一百三十次。赶紧给布洛芬栓剂塞肛。呼吸三十五次。血氧九十。意识目前处于昏睡，能叫醒。先物理降温，额头敷上冰贴。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": "高热惊厥", "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "40.2", "pulseRate": "130", "heartRate": null, "respiratoryRate": "35", "bloodPressure": null, "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": "昏睡", "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "37", "input_text": "“十二床，喝口水看看。嗯，还有点呛。阿司匹林和他汀继续吃。血压一百四、九十。心率八十。瞳孔三毫米，对光反射灵敏。皮肤完好。下午我们要插胃管了，因为你入量不够，得通过鼻饲补充。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "80", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "140/90", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": "完整", "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": "异常", "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "38", "input_text": "“二十五床。胸腔引流瓶里今天出了一百二十毫升，血性液体。呼吸频率二十二，血氧九十五。心率九十。血压一百一、七十。意识清醒。鼓励多咳嗽，把肺里的气鼓起来。疼的话就按止痛泵。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "90", "respiratoryRate": "22", "bloodPressure": "110/70", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": "清楚", "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": "引流管、静脉通路", "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "39", "input_text": "“三号床，天疱疮。全身大面积皮肤破损，渗出液较多。今天继续静脉点滴地塞米松。血压一百二、八十，心率八十五。体温三十七度五。入量要保证，多吃点高质量蛋白。换药的时候动作轻点。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": "天疱疮", "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "37.5", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "85", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "120/80", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": "破损", "limbActivity": null, "catheter": "静脉通路", "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "40", "input_text": "“幺二零送来一个车祸伤。意识模糊。血压八十、四十。心率一百三十。呼吸三十次。血氧测不到。MEWS评分估计有八分。瞳孔对称三点五，反射迟钝。腹部皮肤有大面积青紫破损。快，送抢救室！”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": "其他", "diagnosis": "车祸伤", "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "130", "respiratoryRate": "30", "bloodPressure": "80/40", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": "模糊", "skin": "破损、其他", "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "41", "input_text": "“王大爷，昨晚睡得踏实吗？来，胳膊放平，咱们测个早压。嗯，一百三十二、八十四，挺稳的。体温三十六度六。早起那个苯磺酸氨氯地平吃了吗？记得空腹吃效果好。心率七十四次，呼吸十八。今天感觉头晕好点没？”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "36.6", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "74", "respiratoryRate": "18", "bloodPressure": "132/84", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "42", "input_text": "“张先生，手术后第二天了，今天得试着下床站一站。我先看下指标，血氧饱和度九十九，心率八十二，呼吸二十。体温三十七度幺，有一点点吸收热，没关系。伤口敷料我看下，干燥完好，没有渗液。晚点我扶你走两步。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "37.1", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "82", "respiratoryRate": "20", "bloodPressure": null, "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": "手术切口", "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "43", "input_text": "“阿婆，今早空腹血糖是六点五，控制得不错。体重测了一下，六十二公斤，比上周降了一点点。血压一百二、七十八，脉搏六十八次。体温三十六度四。二甲双胍记得跟着早饭一起吃，别漏了啊。皮肤我看看，脚上没裂口吧？”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "36.4", "pulseRate": "68", "heartRate": null, "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "120/78", "weight": "62", "height": null, "bloodSugar": "6.5", "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "44", "input_text": "“李叔，今天觉得气短好些了吗？我看你这氧流量开的是每分钟两升。测个血氧，九十六，可以的。呼吸二十二次，稍微还是有点快。体温三十六度八，脉搏九十。痰咳出来了吗？要是觉得粘，我等会给你加个雾化。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "36.8", "pulseRate": "90", "heartRate": null, "respiratoryRate": "22", "bloodPressure": null, "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "45", "input_text": "“十二床，今天开始可以喝点米汤了。这瓶泮托拉唑快滴完了，等会儿我来换补液。血压一百一、七十，心率七十六。体温三十六度七。昨晚排便了吗？记录一下，昨天入量一共是一千八百毫升。要注意观察有没有肚子疼。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "36.7", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "76", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "110/70", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": "静脉通路", "diet": "异常", "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "46", "input_text": "“老陈，今天感觉怎么样？胸口不闷了吧。心率六十二次，挺有力的。血压一百二十六、八十二。体温三十六度五。早上的阿司匹林和波立维记得按时吃。我看你输液的地方有点发青，今天换个手打。皮肤完好，没起疹子吧？”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "36.5", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "62", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "126/82", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": "完整", "limbActivity": null, "catheter": "静脉通路", "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "47", "input_text": "“阿姨，跟我说说话，今天早饭吃的什么呀？嗯，口齿比昨天清楚多了。瞳孔我看下，左右对称，都是三毫米，对光反射灵敏。血压一百四十、九十，稍微有点波动。心率七十。阿托伐他汀记得睡前吃，对血管好的。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "70", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "140/90", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "48", "input_text": "“奶奶，咱们翻个身啊。骶尾部皮肤我看看，完好，没红没破，挺好。血压一百二十、七十，脉搏六十四。体温三十六度二。呼吸十六。今天水喝得不少，入量记个八百毫升了。中午想吃点什么？让家属弄点软烂的。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "36.2", "pulseRate": "64", "heartRate": null, "respiratoryRate": "16", "bloodPressure": "120/70", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "limbActivity": null, "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "49", "input_text": "“二十床，明天手术，今天别紧张。体温三十六度八，心率七十八，呼吸十八。血压一百三、八十五。我检查下牵引的重量，位置没动。皮肤完好。今晚十二点以后就禁食禁水了，记住了啊，明早我来给你做术前准备。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "36.8", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "78", "respiratoryRate": "18", "bloodPressure": "130/85", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": "完整", "limbActivity": "异常", "catheter": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "gemini", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
